quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Dͻnhwere no abεn, na bosome no mu apae"
  54,2,"Na sε wͻ’hunu nsεnkyerεnee bi a wͻ’twe wͻn ho (fri ho), na wͻ’ka sε: ”Woi yε nkonyaa anaa naadaasεm a εbetwamu“"
  54,3,"Wͻ’fa no atorɔsɛm, na wͻ’di wͻn apεdeε hunu akyi. Na asεm biara wͻ neberε"
  54,4,Ampa sε (Qur’aan) de amanebͻ a afutuo ne adesua (ahodoͻ pii) wͻ mu abrε wͻn
  54,5,"Adwen ne nimdeε a εkͻ aso mu (wͻ mu), nanso afutuo no ho amma wͻn mfasoͻ"
  54,6,Enti twe wo ho fri wͻn ho. Ɛda a Ɔfrεfoͻ (Israafiil) bεfrε (wͻn) akͻ asεm kεseε mu no
  54,7,(Aniwuo bεma) w’abrε wͻn ani ase; wͻ’bepue afri adakamena no mu tesε mmεbε a wͻ’abͻ asanteε
  54,8,"Wͻ’de mmirika tεntε na εbεkͻ Ɔfrεfoͻ no hͻ. (Saa Da no) boniayεfoͻ no bεka sε: ”Saa Da yi yε Ɛda a emu yε den! “"
  54,9,"Noa nkorͻfoͻ dii wͻn anim kan buu Y’akoa no ᴐtorofo. Wͻ’kaa sε: “Bͻdamfoͻ.“ Wͻ’kasa tiaa no, hunahunaa no, poo no"
  54,10,"Enti osu frεε ne Wura Nyankopͻn sε: (Awurade) “Wͻ’abu afa me so, enti boa (me)“"
  54,11,Enti Ye’buee ͻsoro apono maa nsuo hwie guu pii
  54,12,"Yε’maa nsuwa-nsuwa nso puee wͻ asaase no so, na (ͻsoro ne asaase so) nsuo no hyia bͻͻ mu sεdeε yahyehyε ato hͻ no"
  54,13,Enti Yε’soaa no wͻ (nsuom hyεn a) yεde nnua ne nnadewa na ayε so
  54,14,Na (nsuom hyεn no) nam (nsuo no so) a Y’ani hwε. (Saa nsuyire yi yε) akatua ma obia w’anye annie
  54,15,"Ampa sε, Y’agya de ayε nsεnkyerεnee. Enti obi wͻhͻ a ͻde betu nehofoͻ"
  54,16,Sεdeε M’asotwee ne Mekͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε
  54,17,Ampa sε Y’ama Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no ayε mmrε. Enti obi wͻhͻ a ͻde betu neho foͻ
  54,18,Aad (Nkorͻfoͻ no) faa no atorᴐsԑm. Na sεdeε M’asotwee ne Mekͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε
  54,19,"Nokorε sε, Y’εsomaa mframa denden bi a εbͻ toatoaso baa wͻn so wͻ da bͻne bi mu"
  54,20,Ɛtetee nnipa maa wͻ’yεε sε akyiresua dua bi a yatu aseε da hͻ
  54,21,Sεdeε M’asotwee ne Mekͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε
  54,22,Ampa sε Y’ama Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no ayε mmrε. Enti obi wͻhͻ a ͻde betu neho foͻ
  54,23,Samuudfoͻ no faa kͻkͻbͻ no atorᴐsԑm
  54,24,"Deε wͻ’kaeε ne sε: “Onipa baako pε a ͻwͻ yεn mu na yeni n’akyi? Nokorε sε, εneε na yε’wͻ ͻyera ne abͻdamsεm paa mu"
  54,25,"Enti yεn (dodoͻ yi) mu no, ͻno nko ara na εsεsε yεde Afutusεm no ma no? Daabi, ͻyε nkontomponi, asoͻden (nipa)”"
  54,26,"Ɔkyena wͻ’behunu nea ͻyε nkontomponi, asoͻden (nipa) no"
  54,27,Nokorε sε Yε’resoma yoma bedeε de ayε wͻn nsͻhwε. Enti wodeε hwε wͻn na si aboterε
  54,28,"Na ka kyerε wͻn sε, yakyε nsuo no mu ama (wͻn ne yoma no), obiara bεkͻ nsuo no mu wͻ ne berε (a yahyε ama no) mu"
  54,29,Nanso wͻ’frεε wͻn yͻnko no na ͻfaa (sekan) de wͻͻ (yoma) no kum no
  54,30,Sεdeε M’asotwee ne Mekͻkͻbͻ (huu) siteε
  54,31,"Nokorε sε, Yε’somaa nteamu baako pε na εbaa wͻn soͻ, na wͻ’bεyεε gͻsͻͻ tesε mmabaa a awoͻ na abubu asin-asin a εwͻ mmoa adidieε"
  54,32,Ampa sε Y’ama Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no ayε mmrε. Enti obi wͻhͻ a ͻde betu neho foͻ
  54,33,Lut nkorͻfoͻ no anye kͻkͻbͻ no anni
  54,34,"Nokorε sε Yε’somaa aboͻ nsuo tͻ guu wͻn so, gyesε Lut abusuafoͻ nko ara (na asotwee no bi anka wͻn), Yε’gyee wͻn wͻ anadwo a etwa toᴐ no mu"
  54,35,(Ɛyε) adom a efri Yεn hͻ. Saa ara na Ye’tua wͻn a wͻ’yi (Nyankopͻn) ayε no ka
  54,36,"Ampa sε (Lut) bͻͻ wͻn kͻkͻ wͻ Y’asotwee no ho, nanso wͻn adwen ansi wͻn pi wͻ kͻkͻ bͻ no ho"
  54,37,"Ampa sε wͻ’pεε sε wͻ’hwim n’ahͻhoͻ fri nensam. Na Yefiraa wͻn ani (kaa sε): “Ɛneε monka M’asotwee ne Me kͻkͻbͻ no nhwε “"
  54,38,"Ampa sε, daa asotwee no sͻͻ wͻn mu ahomakye paa"
  54,39,Enti monka M’asotwee ne Mekͻkͻbͻ no nhwε
  54,40,Ampa sε Y’ayε Qur’aan yi nkaekaeε ne emu afutusεm no mmrε. Enti obi wͻ hͻ a ͻde betu neho foͻ
  54,41,Ampa sε kͻkͻbͻ no baa Farao nkorͻfoͻ no hͻ
  54,42,Wͻ’faa Yε’nsεnkyerεnee no nyinaa atorᴐsԑm. Enti Yε’de Otumfoͻ a Otumi ade nyinaa yε no Tumi no pari sͻͻ wͻn mu dendeenden
  54,43,Enti mo (mu) boniayεfoͻ no kyεn woi nom (a y’aseε wͻn no)? Anaasε modeε moanya (bͻhyε) wͻ Twerεsεm no mu sε y’ayi mu afri (asotwee no) mu
  54,44,"Anaasε deε wͻ’ka nesε: ”Yε’deε yε’yε dͻm (kεseε) enti yεbedi nkonim"
  54,45,Yε’bεka wͻn dͻm no agu ama wͻ’adane wͻn akyi adwane
  54,46,"Aane, Dͻnhwere no ne εberε a yεde ahyε wͻn bͻ; na Dͻnhwere no ano yε den na (εyε berε nso) a emu (nsɛm) yε nyono"
  54,47,"Nokorε sε, abͻneεfoͻ no wͻ ͻyera ne abͻdamsεm paa mu"
  54,48,"Ɛda a yεbεtwe wͻn ase wͻ fͻm wͻ wͻn anim so akͻ egya no mu no, (yεbεka akyerε wͻn sε): ”Monka Ogya no atenka no nhwε “"
  54,49,Nokorε sε Yε’de nhyehyεeε na abͻ biribiara
  54,50,"Na Y’ahyεdeε no deε εyε baako pε, εtesε wa’bͻ w’ani prε"
  54,51,Ampa sε Y’asεe (amanfoͻ bi) a na wͻ’te sε mo. Enti obi wͻhͻ a ͻde betu neho foͻ
  54,52,Dwuma a wͻ’die biara no nso y’atwerε no wͻ Nwoma no mu
  54,53,"Biribiara, ketewa ne kεseε nyinaa yatwerε"
  54,54,"Nokorε sε, Nyamesurofoͻ no wͻ Aheman mu ne nsubͻnten ho"
  54,55,"Wͻ Nokorε Ahennwa no ho wͻ Ɔhene Tumfoͻ no a, Otumi adeε nyinaa yε no hͻ"